text: mcheasa robsa anak minmen chea anak del bamphlanh phoumisrok na muoy laey louhtrate trong chattang knong phoumi srok noh nouv anakneasar mneak daembi sautr ayeat robsa yeung aoy puokke sdab sen . haey yeung minmen chea anak bamphlanh phoumisrok namuoy laey leuklengte anak phoumisrok noh chea puok del bampean bonnaoh
